data.description: Welcome to your slice of paradise in the heart of the countryside! This meticulously maintained property spans nearly 2.5 acres, offering the perfect canvas for your rural dreams. Nestled within the lush landscape is a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1900sqft home awaiting your personal touch with detached storage/workshop as well as an outdoor half bath!    Experience the joys of farm life with a pre-built chicken coop ready for your feathered friends to provide fresh eggs year-round. Additionally, there's ample space for a variety of other farm animals, with a designated area thoughtfully crafted for their comfort and well-being.    Nature lovers will delight in the property's natural beauty, boasting a tranquil running creek and lush greenery. Fruit enthusiasts will appreciate the assortment of fruit trees, including mangos, passionfruit, avocados, lemons, and oranges, offering a bounty of flavors right at your doorstep.    The well-maintained yard provides a serene setting for relaxation and outdoor activities, with plenty of room for further customization or expansion to accommodate more farm animals or gardens.    Conveniently located just 15 minutes from major shopping hubs and a short 30-minute drive from downtown Tampa, you can enjoy the tranquility of rural living without sacrificing urban conveniences. Come and experience the best of both worlds at this idyllic country retreat!
